ed="T" n="0808b27"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0808b27"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012751"><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0808003"/>會稽<anchor xml:id="end0808003"/></placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011632">允文</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0808b28"/><persName key="A011632">釋允文</persName>，字<persName key="A011632">執經</persName>，姓<name>朱</name>氏，今<placeName key="PL000000012751"><placeName>秀州</placeName><placeName>嘉禾</placeName></placeName>人也。權<lb
ed="T" n="0808b29"/>輿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g830"/><date key="j20180422018395" from-iso="+0813-02-09" to-iso="+0814-01-28">九歲</date>，厥父云亡，然理命<ptr type="glossary" target="#g833"/>捨文奉佛。師授<pb ed="T" n="0808c" xml:id="T50.2061.0808c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0808c01"/>《維摩》、《法華》二經，敏速之性，再稔皆通，高達之<lb
ed="T" n="0808c02"/>士謂之重理<ptr type="glossary" target="#g330"/>耳。或戲問<persName key="A011632">文</persName>曰：「爾出家之後，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c03"/>擬營何事業乎？」率然對曰：「當陟蓮華臺而<lb
ed="T" n="0808c04"/>作師子吼。」或訶誚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1193"/>之曰：「耆宿前敢爾？」或曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0808c05"/>「志欲得大，<ref type="person" target="#A011632">此子</ref>將來未易測也。」至<date key="j20205812020964" from-iso="+0820-01-23" to-iso="+0821-02-09">十六歲</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c06"/>削頂周羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1280"/>，披安陀會<ptr type="glossary" target="#g834"/>。相次裹足<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1360"/>西上，投<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩<lb
ed="T" n="0808c07"/>山</placeName>臨壇大德<persName key="A011633">遠<roleName>和尚</roleName></persName>邊，獲無作法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>，時<date key="j20231502023504" from-iso="+0827-02-04" to-iso="+0828-01-24">年二十<lb
ed="T" n="0808c08"/>三</date>矣。<date key="j20232392023327" from-iso="+0827-05-04" to-iso="+0827-07-31">是夏</date>即就<placeName key="PL000000042189">中京</placeName>攻<placeName key="PL000000024082">相部</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>律宗<ptr target="#n911"/>并《中觀<lb
ed="T" n="0808c09"/>論》<ptr target="#n1551"/>，補衣<ptr target="#n1863"/>分衛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g602"/>，寒燠四周。既扣義門，必入師<lb
ed="T" n="0808c10"/>室，玄樞律範，尤見精微。<date from-iso="+0831-02-20" key="j20246272024981" to-iso="+0832-02-09"><name>大和</name>五年</date>，為思定<lb
ed="T" n="0808c11"/>省，忽歎歸歟。既返故鄉，淹時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g839"/>寢疾，<anchor xml:id="beg0808sgsz7"/>未<anchor xml:id="end0808sgsz7"/>遑講<lb
ed="T" n="0808c12"/>唱。後聞<placeName key="PL000000011627"><placeName>錢塘</placeName><placeName>天竺寺</placeName></placeName>講《大涅槃經》，蔚為勝<lb
ed="T" n="0808c13"/>集，<persName key="A011632">文</persName>往學焉。星歲未周，鋒芒且露。<date from-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282026811" to-iso="+0837-02-12"><name>開成</name>元年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c14"/>因遊<placeName key="PL000000014411">台嶠</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g844"/>，止息<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000013176">嘉祥寺</placeName>，眾藉清芬，甄<lb
ed="T" n="0808c15"/>命敷其經律。<persName key="A011632">文</persName>戢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g48"/>約聽徒，頗為嚴毅，常訓<lb
ed="T" n="0808c16"/>之曰：「夫苾芻行非家法、具足別解脫律儀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g848"/>、眾<lb
ed="T" n="0808c17"/>同分<ptr type="glossary" target="#g851"/>，是其自性<ptr type="glossary" target="#g857"/>於其形色精進<ptr type="glossary" target="#g854"/>故、怖畏<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g856"/>故、<lb
ed="T" n="0808c18"/>防守故。如是，方疾得道果矣！不然，則弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0808c19"/>既墮，師道徒施。」聞其警策，有涕泗交橫，悛<lb
ed="T" n="0808c20"/>心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g858"/>革行，思過半<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1565"/>矣。<date from-iso="+0843-02-07" key="j20289972029351" to-iso="+0844-01-27"><name>會昌</name>三年</date>，移居<placeName key="PL000000013212">靜林寺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c21"/>專以《涅槃》宣導。屬乎<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>澄汰，例被搜揚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g859"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0808c22"/>晝披縫掖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g868"/>之衣，夜著縵條<ptr type="glossary" target="#g878"/>之服，罔虧僧行，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c23"/>唯逭<ptr type="glossary" target="#g503"/>俗譏。<date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612031609" notAfter-iso="+0850-04-03"><name>大中</name>伊始</date>，復振空門，重整法儀，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c24"/>乃隷名<placeName key="PL000000013226">開元寺</placeName>三十人數。<date from-iso="+0853-02-16" key="j20326592033012" to-iso="+0854-02-04">七年</date>，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013226">寺</ref>之耆舊命<lb
ed="T" n="0808c25"/>講律乘。<date from-iso="+0876-07-29" key="j20412232041310" to-iso="+0876-10-24"><name>乾符</name>三年丙申秋</date>，罷講，覽藏經。以<lb
ed="T" n="0808c26"/><date key="j20434072043407" when-iso="+0882-07-22"><name>中和</name>二年壬寅六月二十九日</date>微疾作而長逝，<lb
ed="T" n="0808c27"/>享齡七十有八，法臘五十五。<date key="j20434192043419" when-iso="+0882-08-03">其年七月十二<lb
ed="T" n="0808c28"/>日</date>葬于<placeName key="PL000000058063">石奇山</placeName>之陽。遺言不許封樹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g890"/>也。初<lb
ed="T" n="0808c29"/><persName key="A011632">文</persName>講演升座，學徒畏憚，<anchor xml:id="beg0808sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>暗</sic><corr>喑</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0808sgsz9"/>嗚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g881"/>之際，人皆披靡，<pb ed="T" n="0809a" xml:id="T50.2061.0809a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809a01"/>乃戒威德之若是。於<placeName key="PL000000013176">嘉祥</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013212">靜林</placeName>、今<placeName key="PL000000013226">大善</placeName>三寺，<lb
ed="T" n="0809a02"/>講<persName key="A000747">相</persName>疏<ptr target="#n903"/>二十七座，大經二十五座。其為人<lb
ed="T" n="0809a03"/>也：貌古而脩長，銳頂而䵟黑，執持密緻，振鷺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g891"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809a04"/>在庭，未足方其潔也。然亦獵涉<name>儒</name>、<name>墨</name>，慕<lb
ed="T" n="0809a05"/><persName key="A004029">白傅</persName>自作誌<ptr target="#n1864"/>，預著《方墳銘》，藏于篋笥。門人<lb
ed="T" n="0809a06"/><persName key="A011634">懷益</persName>，因尋閱<persName key="A011632">文</persName>籍，見而悲咽，遂從<ref type="person" target="#A011632">先師</ref>之<lb
ed="T" n="0809a07"/>志，建小塔焉。後門人<persName key="A011635">懷肅</persName>、<persName key="A011636">思寂</persName>命名德<persName key="A009895">虛<lb
ed="T" n="0809a08"/>受</persName>增加後序。<persName key="A001910">贊寧</persName>登<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>，曾<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz1"/><persName key="A011632">文</persName>真相，見<lb
ed="T" n="0809a09"/>法孫<persName key="A011637">可翔</persName>，苦節進修，叶杜多<ptr type="glossary" target="#g566"/>之行。故熟其事<lb
ed="T" n="0809a10"/>迹也。</p>
